query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 0
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('acumatica',
'asp.net-core-webapi',
'automatic-ref-counting',
'azure-web-sites',
'batch-processing',
'forms-authentication',
'generator',
'interpolation',
'manifolds',
'mod-wsgi',
'nonlinear-optimization',
'require',
'wso2esb',
'wxwidgets',
'xslt-2.0')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'magento',
'math',
'ru',
'stackoverflow')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
